dict.key: To get started with a fresh extension, go to the File menu and choose New > Target. When you're asked to choose a template, select iOS > Application Extension > Action Extension, then click Next. For the name just call it Extension, make sure Action Type is set to "Presents User Interface", then click Finish. To get started with a fresh extension, go to the File menu and choose New > Target.
